    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's ready to hit the road! This car is a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a great price. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a reliable performer that gets the job done every single day. It's the perfect balance of affordability and utility\u2014come see why this well-loved car is such a great value!",
