    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly showroom-quality vehicle. This specimen has been maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting a flawless finish and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
