    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey neighbor! Hard to believe I'm doing this, but I'm letting go of my absolute favorite ride. If you're looking for something that feels like it just left the showroom, this is it! I\u2019ve babied this car from the start, and it shows in every polished curve and every mile. It\u2019s in truly pristine shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s about as close to perfect as you can get. She runs like a dream and catches eyes at every light. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who appreciates a well-loved machine. Swing by, let's grab a coffee, and talk cars!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Up for acquisition is a surgically maintained E46 M3, a true purist\u2019s spec. The S54 powerplant pulls with relentless linear delivery, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for total peace of mind. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to handle the increased torsional loads of spirited driving. Every bushing has been swapped for high-durometer polyurethane, sharpening the turn-in response and eliminating any hint of deflection. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains that factory-fresh tactile feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine optimized for peak mechanical sympathy and raw performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    }
